%html
  %head
    %title C-3PO
    = stylesheet_link_tag    "application", media: "all"
    = javascript_include_tag "application"
    = csrf_meta_tags
  %body.body
    = render 'shared/navbar'
    .col-md-2.left-workspace
      #notices
        - if not user_signed_in?
          .alert-danger
            Robin, is this you? Think I need to renew these optical modules.
        - elsif flash[:notice].present? || flash[:alert].present?
          - if flash[:notice].present?
            .alert-success
              = flash[:notice]
          - if flash[:alert].present?
            .alert-danger
              = flash[:alert]
        - else
          .alert-danger
            I'm speechless.
    .col-md-10.center-workspace
      .base-container
        = yield
    .col-md-12.footer
      %center
        Â© Robin Neumann | 2013 | Be aware. He's nearly passing the Turing-Test.
